> 1. Copy this file to your project root as `CLAUDE.md`.
> 2. Replace `<PROJECT_NAME>` with your project's display name.
> 3. Pair it with the sibling `.claude/settings.json.template` (copy that one
>    to `~/.claude/settings.json` -- or to `<project>/.claude/settings.json`
